{"tid":2253383,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"5名受家屬委託律師到鹽田看守所尋求與當事人見面","createTime":"2020-10-22T06:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T07:54:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b6d6102cb1d8afb8e240654ee3c0cb25a16ec764","tid":2253383,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"涉嫌偷越邊境的12名港人仍被羈押在深圳，5名受家屬委託的律師，早上到鹽田看守所尋求與當事人見面。<br />\n<br />\n5名受委託律師分別代表李宇軒、喬映瑜、黃臨福、郭子麟和鄧棨然。郭子麟的律師藺其磊表示，看守所指郭子麟已經委託兩名律師，不會安排探視，亦不准律師見當事人核實情況是否屬實。<br />\n<br />\n代表黃臨福的律師盧廷閣表示，當局同樣指黃臨福已經委託兩名律師，但當事人未成年，他質疑有關委託是否有效。<br />\n<br />\n律師宋玉生和盧思位分別指，已經報警要求派人到場處理，同時將就無法會見當事人，控告和投訴有關部門。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556104-20201022.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556104-20201022.htm&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPRPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=d79b8304\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1556104-20201022.htm&h=1c7aebed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1556104-20201022.htm</a>"},{"pid":"647a81a2ff5d7878b65ec8fb6f8619baf36d51b2","tid":2253383,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:15:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf47a4159d74f385ad322a4f5d6ffc73311fe093","tid":2253383,"uid":19501,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T06:16:27.000Z","msg":"respect維權律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5acfd03d4cab8cd6fee29e6346db7699170685","tid":2253383,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"647a81a2ff5d7878b65ec8fb6f8619baf36d51b2","t